explanation: Labour Together Limited is a think tank closely associated with the Labour Party in the UK. It was founded in 2015 to support the party's electoral strategies and policy development. The organization focuses on political strategy, public opinion measurement, and policy formulation, particularly in relation to Labour's governance and electoral success. As a think tank, it engages in research and advocacy to influence political discourse and party policy, making it distinct from traditional political organizations or businesses. More information can be found on their official website [Labour Together](https://www.labourtogether.uk/).
